A Woodcutter's Love<br />The tallest Southern tree<br />Affords no shade for me.<br />The maiden on the stream<br />Can but be found in dream.<br />For me the stream's too wide<br />To reach the other side<br />As River Han's too long<br />To cross its current strong.<br />Of the trees in the wood
